data.description: Talk about room to spread out! There's over 1700 sq foot of finished living space in this 1.5 story home! Conveniently located close to downtown and directly across the street from the park and city pool! Character throughout! This home features original hardwood floors throughout the kitchen, dining room and living room. The kitchen offers stainless steel appliances and an ample amount of cabinets. Beautiful built in cabinets separate the dining area and living room! The main floor has one bedroom, plus a bonus room. Upstairs you will find 2 additional nice size bedrooms with vaulted ceilings, and an additional full bathroom. 2 car detached garage with extra work space! Multi-story decks on the back of the home that offers great space for entertaining, and a separate entrance to the 2nd level! Schedule your showing today and see all that this one has to offer!
